<h1>Youngest director</h1>

<% if @youngest.dob.present? %>
  <p>The youngest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= @youngest.id %>"><%= @youngest.name %></a>, born on <%= @youngest.dob.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %>.</p>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>
<% else %>
  <p>There are no directors in the database with a date of birth.</p>
<% end %>
